{"title":"山村钟声——故乡诗抄","authors":["李学鳌"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":12,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村钟声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——故乡诗抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李学鳌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当当！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当当！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清脆的钟声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把山村的天空叫亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锨明晃晃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦田浇冻水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见万斤粮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直奔养猪场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点火煮饲料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猪肥肉膘长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身背拾粪筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕村转三周，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粪堆指天上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托儿所里去帮忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨晚刚学的新民歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又飞到孩子们小嘴上。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当当！当当！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘹亮的神曲在山中回响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡人欢笑着前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥一轮火红的太阳！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}